1571
01:13:25,652 --> 01:13:27,763
Now, in our residential sector...

1572
01:13:27,863 --> 01:13:29,031
VINNIE: Mark, it's not a Q and A.

1573
01:13:29,156 --> 01:13:30,808
...our rollout of those
variable rate packages

1574
01:13:30,908 --> 01:13:32,534
