1595
01:14:25,045 --> 01:14:26,046
(ALL LAUGHING)

1596
01:14:26,672 --> 01:14:29,324
- MAN: Our subprime department is fine.
- No, I'm not doing anything right now.

1597
01:14:29,424 --> 01:14:30,951
MAN: As I was saying,
our residential department...

1598
01:14:31,051 --> 01:14:32,219
How are the kids?

1599
01:14:32,344 --> 01:14:34,705
MAN:...consumers
reacted to our packages...

1600
01:14:34,805 --> 01:14:36,457
Mark Baum really did that.

1601
01:14:36,557 --> 01:14:37,791
When we were in Vegas, he did that.

1602
01:14:37,891 --> 01:14:40,060
