01:15:11,383 --> 01:15:13,160
It's easy to see that delinquencies

1614
01:15:13,260 --> 01:15:16,121
and default rates
are on the rise right now.

1615
01:15:16,221 --> 01:15:18,390
Could you please stop
being such a buzzkill, dude?

1616
01:15:18,765 --> 01:15:21,293
We didn't bring you out here
to talk about work, bro.

1617
01:15:21,393 --> 01:15:22,836
